actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT
	"carId",
	category,
	"itemId" AS id,
	CASE 
		WHEN "itemId" BETWEEN 1 AND 41 THEN 
			CASE "itemId"
				WHEN 1 THEN '南梦宫白表'
				WHEN 2 THEN '黄表'
				WHEN 3 THEN '红表'
				WHEN 4 THEN '特殊表'
				WHEN 5 THEN '蓝表'
				WHEN 6 THEN '碳表'
				WHEN 7 THEN '金属 - 黑'
				WHEN 8 THEN '金属 - 红'
				WHEN 9 THEN '赛博 - 蓝'
				WHEN 10 THEN '赛博 - 红'
				WHEN 11 THEN '会员 - 淡蓝'
				WHEN 12 THEN '会员 = 深红'
				WHEN 13 THEN '森林 - 深绿'
				WHEN 14 THEN '森林 - 棕色'
				WHEN 15 THEN '沙漠 - 深色'
				WHEN 16 THEN '沙漠 - 浅色'
				WHEN 17 THEN '海盗 - 黄色'
				WHEN 18 THEN '海盗 - 蓝色'
				WHEN 19 THEN '火 - 1'
				WHEN 20 THEN '火 - 2'
				WHEN 21 THEN '通行 - 银色'
				WHEN 22 THEN '通行 - 金色'
				WHEN 23 THEN '蒸汽朋克 - 黄色'
				WHEN 24 THEN '蒸汽朋克 - 金色'
				WHEN 25 THEN '龙 - 金色'
				WHEN 26 THEN '龙 - 蓝色'
				WHEN 27 THEN '线条 - 蓝色'
				WHEN 28 THEN '线条 - 橙色'
				WHEN 29 THEN 'Pro'
				WHEN 30 THEN '经典'
				WHEN 31 THEN '数码 - 蓝'
				WHEN 32 THEN '高端 - 红'
				WHEN 33 THEN '数字 - 黄'
				WHEN 34 THEN '高端 - 黄'
				WHEN 35 THEN '太阳 - 1'
				WHEN 36 THEN '太阳 - 2'
				WHEN 37 THEN '月亮 - 1'
				WHEN 38 THEN '月亮 - 2'
				WHEN 39 THEN '宇宙 - 1'
				WHEN 40 THEN '宇宙 - 2'
				WHEN 41 THEN '天狼星数字表'
				ELSE 'Unknown Item'
			END
		ELSE 'Unknown Item'
	END AS name,
	CASE 
		WHEN "itemId" BETWEEN 1 AND 41 THEN 
			CASE "itemId"
				WHEN 1 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fb8531f144a01007aa5ce9.png'
				WHEN 2 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fb8564f144a01007aaa6c2.png'
				WHEN 3 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fb8564f144a01007aaa6e9.png'
				WHEN 4 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fb8564f144a01007aaa729.png'
				WHEN 5 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fb8565f144a01007aaa77c.png'
				WHEN 6 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fb8565f144a01007aaa7a7.png'
				WHEN 7 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fbf8cdf144a0100726df52.png'
				WHEN 8 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fbf8eff144a010072700ec.png'
				WHEN 9 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fbf908f144a01007271715.png'

				WHEN 38 THEN 'https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/63fc0295f144a0100733ad96.png'

				ELSE 'null'
			END

	END AS img
FROM public."CarItem"
WHERE "carId" = {{SelectCarId.selectedOptionValue}} AND category = 15
ORDER BY "itemId" ASC;
